These are Puzzles for 7x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-1::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, coffee, iced-tea
There 3 different types of food: watermelon, broccoli, pear
The people have 3 different hobbies: singing, collecting, camping
The people have 3 different jobs:  pilot, project-manager, software-developer
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: gospel, house, metal
There are 3 different nationalities: french, argentine, malaysian
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: soccer, ice-hockey, snowboarding
 1. the person who's sport is soccer is the argentine##1
 2. the person who's sport is snowboarding is the software-developer##1
 3. the person drinking iced-tea is between the malaysian and the person drinking coffee##2
 4. the fan of house is on the left of the french##1
 5. the project-manager is the person eating pear##1
 6. the person who's hobby is camping is the french##1
 7. the person who's hobby is camping is on the left of the person eating watermelon##1
 8. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left of the fan of gospel##1
 9. the person who's sport is soccer is on the left of the project-manager##1
10. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |       3       |
| Beverage      | coffee    | iced-tea   | almond-milk           |
| Food          | broccoli       | pear    | watermelon         |
| Hobby         | collecting    | camping  | singing        |
| Job           | pilot | project-manager   | software-developer      |
| Music-Genre   | house        | metal    | gospel       |
| Nationality   | argentine     | french  | malaysian       |
| Sport         | soccer     | ice-hockey | snowboarding |

