.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-2::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: 7up, hot-chocolate, tea
There 3 different types of food: cauliflower, grapes, pumpkin
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: superhero, time-travel, fantasy
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: funk, country, trance
There are 3 different nationalities: german, canadian, brazilian
3 different pets are kept: hamster, chinchilla, bird
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: ice-hockey, volleyball, handball
 1. the owner of the bird is the canadian##1
 2. the owner of the bird is the person watching fantasy movies##1
 3. the person watching fantasy movies is on the right of the owner of the hamster##1
 4. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is between the person drinking hot-chocolate and the person drinking 7up##2
 5. the brazilian is on the far left##1
 6. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the fan of funk##1
 7. the fan of country is on the left of the person who's sport is handball##1
 8. the person eating cauliflower is the person watching superhero movies##1
 9. the person watching fantasy movies is on the right of the fan of trance##1
10. the owner of the bird is on the left of the person eating pumpkin##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |       3       |
| Beverage      | 7up   | tea    | hot-chocolate         |
| Food          | cauliflower    | grapes | pumpkin          |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero  | fantasy  | time-travel     |
| Music-Genre   | trance       | country      | funk         |
| Nationality   | brazilian      | canadian   | german    |
| Pet           | hamster        | bird      | chinchilla         |
| Sport         | volleyball | ice-hockey  | handball |

