.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-3::.
There 3 different types of food: mango, plum, artichoke
The people have 3 different hobbies: cooking, woodworking, camping
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: mystery, comedy, horror
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: metal, house, trance
There are 3 different nationalities: malaysian, indonesian, australian
3 different pets are kept: lizard, horse, rat
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: skiing, snowboarding, badminton
 1. the person eating plum is the owner of the horse##1
 2. the australian is the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
 3. the person watching mystery movies is the person eating artichoke##1
 4. the person watching comedy movies is the owner of the horse##1
 5. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the left of the person who's sport is badminton##1
 6. the person watching comedy movies is on the left of the person who's sport is badminton##1
 7. the person who's hobby is camping is between the indonesian and the fan of trance##2
 8. the indonesian is on the left of the fan of metal##1
 9. the owner of the horse is on the right of the person who's sport is skiing##1
10. the owner of the rat is on the right of the person eating plum##1
11. the indonesian is the person eating artichoke##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |      3       |
| Food          | artichoke      | plum      | mango      |
| Hobby         | cooking   | camping | woodworking |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery | comedy    | horror          |
| Music-Genre   | house       | metal      | trance          |
| Nationality   | indonesian    | malaysian  | australian      |
| Pet           | lizard   | horse  | rat        |
| Sport         | skiing  | snowboarding   | badminton     |

