The people prefer 3 different music-genres: r&b, blues, reggae
There are 3 different nationalities: japanese, canadian, russian
3 different pets are kept: horse, goat, dog
 1. the owner of the goat is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
 2. the person drinking tea is the russian##1
 3. the owner of the dog is on the left of the person watching animation movies##1
 4. the fan of blues is on the right of the fan of r&b##1
 5. the fan of r&b is between the person watching musical movies and the person drinking tea##2
 6. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person who's hobby is reading##1
 7. the fan of r&b is the person who's hobby is singing##1
 8. the paramedic is the owner of the dog##1
 9. the person drinking juice is between the paramedic and the designer##2
10. the russian is on the left of the canadian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2        |       3       |
| Beverage      | tea | juice           | cola      |
| Hobby         | reading       | singing         | woodworking       |
