3 different pets are kept: cat, frog, goat
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: biathlon, snowboarding, parkour
The people use 3 different means of transport: roller, train, trike
 1. the person eating pepper is on the left of the person driving the trike##1
 2. the person driving the roller is on the left of the owner of the cat##1
 3. the person drinking iced-tea is the person who's sport is parkour##1
 4. the person drinking mirinda is on the far right##1
 5. the person who's sport is parkour is between the person who's sport is snowboarding and the fan of trance##2
 6. the person who's sport is parkour is between the person who's sport is biathlon and the owner of the goat##2
 7. the person driving the roller is between the person eating papaya and the person drinking tea##2
 8. the fan of classical is on the right of the fan of rock##1
 9. the entrepreneur is on the right of the fan of rock##1
10. the paramedic is the person eating papaya##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |       2       |     3      |
