4. the person driving the airplane is on the right of the person watching adventure movies##1
5. the person eating corn is between the person watching adventure movies and the owner of the rabbit##2
6. the person drinking milk is the owner of the frog##1
7. the person watching musical movies is in the middle##1
8. the person who's hobby is collecting is the fan of house##1
9. the person who's hobby is drawing is between the person drinking soy-milk and the owner of the frog##2

