10. the owner of the frog is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1
11. the person driving the trike is the turkish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |
| Beverage      | soy-milk | hot-chocolate      | sprite      |
| Hobby         | skydiving     | gardening     | board-games  |
| Movie-Genre   | satire | action  | thriller |
| Nationality   | french  | pakistani     | turkish |
| Pet           | snake        | frog | ferret     |
| Sport         | cricket    | snowboarding | golf   |
| Transport     | ship        | helicopter        | trike   |

