.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-18::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, sprite, cola
There 3 different types of food: lemon, potato, raspberry
The people have 3 different hobbies: reading, fishing, card-games
The people have 3 different jobs:  software-developer, engineer, social-worker
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: comedy, hot-chocolatesy, drama
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: baseball, parkour, sailing
The people use 3 different means of transport: quad-bike, taxi, train
1. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the social-worker##1
2. the person driving the train is on the right of the person eating raspberry##1
3. the person eating potato is on the left of the software-developer##1
4. the person who's sport is baseball is between the person watching comedy movies and the engineer##2
5. the person eating raspberry is between the social-worker and the person who's hobby is card-games##2
6. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the right of the person eating raspberry##1
7. the person who's sport is parkour is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
8. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
9. the person watching hot-chocolatesy movies is on the left of the software-developer##1

.:: Answer ::.
