2. the person who's sport is handball is on the right of the person watching mystery movies##1
3. the person who's sport is swimming is on the right of the person who's sport is handball##1
4. the person watching action movies is on the right of the person driving the trike##1
5. the person eating lime is between the person drinking soy-milk and the person who's hobby is writing##2
6. the person eating cucumber is on the right of the fan of classical##1
7. the person drinking water is on the right of the fan of house##1
8. the person driving the jet-ski is the person watching action movies##1
9. the person who's hobby is writing is on the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##1

