.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-20::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: water, coffee, soy-milk
There 3 different types of food: onion, strawberry, mango
The people have 3 different jobs:  freelancer, musician, entrepreneur
There are 3 different nationalities: egyptian, nigerian, chinese
3 different pets are kept: cat, hamster, ferret
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: rowing, skateboarding, snowboarding
The people use 3 different means of transport: scooter, trike, airplane
1. the person drinking water is the person eating mango##1
2. the person driving the airplane is the person who's sport is rowing##1
3. the freelancer is between the person drinking soy-milk and the owner of the ferret##2
4. the egyptian is on the left of the person driving the airplane##1
5. the owner of the cat is on the left of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
6. the person driving the trike is on the left of the person driving the airplane##1
7. the musician is the person eating onion##1
8. the owner of the ferret is on the left of the owner of the cat##1
9. the nigerian is between the person eating onion and the person driving the scooter##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |    3     |
| Beverage      | coffee    | water       | soy-milk      |
| Food          | onion   | mango   | strawberry  |
| Job           | musician  | freelancer | entrepreneur    |
| Nationality   | egyptian   | nigerian     | chinese  |
| Pet           | ferret     | cat        | hamster |
| Sport         | skateboarding | rowing   | snowboarding  |
| Transport     | trike    | airplane     | scooter      |

 